  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nAmount input field has limit of 10 characters. When user enters the number the limit may be satisfied but after reformatting the number according to locale (when editing), it may be wider than the limit.\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nGo to community settings, permissions, create new permission, who holds section -> add asset, as amount enter 1000000000, click on the amount in \"who holds section\" to edit\r\n\r\n\r\n<!-- example: step 1. do X step 2. do Y etc.. -->\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nLimit should be satisfied also after reformatting according to the locale\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nAdding empty spaces or other separators breaks the limit.\r\n\r\n\r\n[Kazam_screencast_00126.webm](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20650004/222411150-5d93914c-f534-4761-86d0-3e8aeb743ee6.webm)\r\n",
